review: I consulted Dr Prasanna online for of acute back pain, where I was not able to even stand straight or walk without support and was experiencing bad pain. He explained, what could have led to this condition, suggested Dos and Don'ts. I was able to walk normally within 2 days of taking the prescribed Medicines and within 5 days of the course, I am completely fine. i was given exercises to do regularly. I never hoped it to get better with online consultation. The treatment was exceptional I should say.

review: i was in pain in my wrist .. i had fell from the cycle and could not pick up slight weights also from my right hand .. i showed 2 other doctors before him and they said the wrist will heal and no medication was required .. but till 3 weeks the pain was ther .. but doctor prasanna understood my problem and gave me medicines and withen 5 days my pain had gone 95% and i was back to doing my normal routines .. i am very thank full to him as for 3 weeks i was not able to do anything from my right hand ..wonderfull experience

review: My mother-in-law (79 years) had lower back pain after a fall; she had pain and unable to move much! We contacted Dr. Prasanna via Practo! We had a video consultation with him, and it was a great experience! The medicines prescribed by him worked well, and my mother-in-law was feeling better in a couple of days! We had follow-up sessions as well, and the experience was equally good!
